question: What is the rank of Mumbai in terms of the highest number of digital transactions in India in 2019 according to the report of “Wordline India Digital Payments 2019”?
explanation: Mumbai ranked third in terms of the highest number of digital transactions in India in 2019 according to the report of “Wordline India Digital Payments 2019”. Bengaluru ranked first among cities. The state of Maharashtra ranked first among the states.
